'''public library'''
#Meant to be a culture forum for all community members, and could be with or without fees. Information services are provided beside many other culture intertaiment, e.g. cinema, theatre etc. Special area are dedicated to children for reading and some activities (e.g. story teller). Public library could provide some special information services for business people and commercial activities with special fees.

